  "body": "I tried to update the NetworkPolicy Spec field with more ingress rules but got `Forbidden: updates to networkpolicy spec are forbidden.`\r\nIt seems NetworkPolicy does not allow update on Spec https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/3e3ff447d28075904177d3e7cad73e405b271de5/pkg/apis/extensions/validation/validation.go#L836\r\nThis means if I want to have more ingress rules, I will have to add those in a new networkpolicy in the same namespace.\r\nAny reason why I should not add those in the existing one(update the existing networkpolicy)? Thanks!",
